metadata.name: Parametrical Fashion #1
metadata.description:
It is a combination of art, creativity and artificial intelligence. Unparalleled beauty is everywhere, we just need to see it better. I'm an architect and I've been using graphic software like Maya, 3D Max, Houdini, etc. for years, but NFT and blockchain show us a new world of their capabilities.
4267 x 4267 Pixel
